MBOMBELA – According to the Department of Community, Safety, Security and Liaison spokesman Joseph Mabuza, the accident happened on the Schoemanskloof Road next to Joubert and Son’s Farm at about 09:00. “This crash happened a few minutes after the biker clocked 283 kilometres per hour on the N4 where our officers were conducting a speed check. Unfortunately the biker did not survive the crash.” Nobody was injured in the Sedan.